CustomField.description: The shipping wizard defaults the units to LB/IN. If this checkbox is checked, the shipping wizard will default to KG/CM, even for domestic shipments. This is applicable to the entire org for all created shipmate preferences.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The shipping wizard defaults the units to LB/IN. If this checkbox is checked, the shipping wizard will default to KG/CM, even for domestic shipments. This is applicable to the entire org for all created shipmate preferences.
CustomField.label: Default Units to KG/CM
